Cores&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Improvement&lt;/em&gt;: Visual Improvement for the devices&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img data-cfsrc="https://files.gamebanana.com/img/ss/wips/67b28a5fb2b34.jpg" src="https://files.gamebanana.com/img/ss/wips/67b28a5fb2b34.jpg"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Experience TOTK with Sheikah Technology&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Ever wanted to experience playing "Tears of the Kingdom" (TOTK) with the same feeling as Sheikah technology from "Breath of the Wild" (BOTW)? This mod aims to convert all Zonai devices, structures, weapons, and effects to fit more of the Sheikah aesthetic.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Check the discord of the mod, here you will see in progress content of the mod, give feedback, post your ideas and more!&lt;br&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="anchor_edefb8 anchorUnderlineOnHover_edefb8" href="https://discord.gg/CSFDBnXkB8"&gt;https://discord.gg/CSFDBnXkB8&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The mod will be released in several waves (The progress bar its about the wave in development):&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1st Wave:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; All devices replaced with a Sheikah aesthetic.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;First wave finished!!! It took me 2 and half months to finish this part.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Also, here are all the icons that represent each changed model &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;(If you want to experience it without spoilers, don't click on them)&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span class="Spoiler"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-cfsrc="https://files.gamebanana.com/img/ss/wips/67f87e4fc7e08.jpg" src="https://files.gamebanana.com/img/ss/wips/67f87e4fc7e08.jpg"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Creator's note:&lt;/b&gt; Thanks to all the Discord members for helping me understand the mods correctly, and especially thanks to member Alciel for offering so much help and expertise.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Also try this mod as a recomendation, it fits the style of this mod so well:&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/573450" class="SelectedElement"&gt;https://gamebanana.com/mods/573450&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Upcoming Waves:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;2nd Wave:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; All weapons, shields, and more replaced.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Between 1st and 2nd Waves:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; Ultrahand and Link's Zonai abilities effects are replaced to fit more of the Sheikah tech aesthetic.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;3rd Wave:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; A separate standalone mod with new structures to get the new devices to work with the Zonai ones (Possibly with new mechanics).</description>
